		<itunes:summary>This is a special story reading by Maria Fernanda Macimiani from Argentina. You can find the complete text of the story here.

Maria is the author of  "Amigos estelares" and also the editor of Léeme Un Cuento, a marvelous Spanish-language web site filled with original children's stories and other great kid content like lullabies and tongue twisters. There are even short stories written by kids for kids. Check it out!

