		<description><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/picresized_1226837399_eleena2.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-339" title="picresized_1226837399_eleena2" src="http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/picresized_1226837399_eleena2.jpg" alt="" /></a><strong>¡Hola amigos!</strong></p>
<p>Mommy has created a new <a title="Find Cody's Cuentos on Facebook!" href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Codys-Cuentos/34792789191?ref=s" target="_self">page for Cody&#8217;s Cuentos</a> inside Facebook, a popular Internet web site where humans hang out. Supposedly no dogs are allowed, but we&#8217;re going to see about&#8230;</p>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/picresized_1226837399_eleena2.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-339" title="picresized_1226837399_eleena2" src="http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/picresized_1226837399_eleena2.jpg" alt="" /></a><strong>¡Hola amigos!</strong></p>
<p>Mommy has created a new <a title="Find Cody's Cuentos on Facebook!" href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Codys-Cuentos/34792789191?ref=s" target="_self">page for Cody&#8217;s Cuentos</a> inside Facebook, a popular Internet web site where humans hang out. Supposedly no dogs are allowed, but we&#8217;re going to see about that! <img src='http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif' alt=':D' class='wp-smiley' />  Anyway, this page in Facebook is a place where you guys, the listeners of Cody&#8217;s Cuentos, can meet one another and also get to talk with mommy and me. It&#8217;s also a place where you can ask questions, leave comments, feedback and suggestions. Also, if you want to leave me an occasional fan letter or a virtual dog biscuit, that would be cool too. <img src='http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p>Speaking of fans&#8230;.we need you to drop by and make it official and become a fan of the podcast. Why do you have to do that? Well, Mommy says that whenever we have some news to tell you, we can send you a message through Facebook. She doesn&#8217;t want me to spill the beans yet but there are a few special stories, something she calls  &#8220;a mini-series,&#8221; that she&#8217;s getting ready to podcast early next year. So if you&#8217;re one of my fans on Facebook, I&#8217;ll make sure you hear about this kind of stuff as soon as Mommy says it&#8217;s OK.</p>
<p>Never heard of Facebook? No worries.  <a href="http://www.facebook.com" target="_self">Facebook</a> is an Internet social networking site for humans to stay in touch with their friends and family and make new friends at the same time. It&#8217;s also free to join.</p>
<p>Click on the big &#8220;Facebook&#8221; below to go directly to my Cody&#8217;s Cuentos page. ¡Gracias y nos vemos allí!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Codys-Cuentos/34792789191"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-333" title="facebook_badge" src="http://www.codyscuentos.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/facebook_badge.jpg" alt="" width="498" height="120" /></a></p>
