			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hello all,</p>
<p>The podcast is on hiatus and will be back sometime in the fall. Thank you all for listening and leaving comments about episodes from Season 1. Spread the word and tell all your friends and relatives who might enjoy the program about Cody&#8217;s Cuentos. Be sure to subscribe to the <a title="Cody's Cuentos feed address" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/codyscuentos" target="_self">RSS feed</a> or to <a title="Cody on iTunes" href="http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=275509234" target="_self">iTunes</a> to make sure you get the first episode of Season 2 as soon as it goes online later this fall.  I will be posting occasionally here on the blog until then.</p>
<p>¡Hasta luego!</p>
