		<description><![CDATA[<p>If you&#8217;re into social media and have a Twitter account, you can now keep tabs on Cody there. His little paws will be tapping out messages over there whenever the mood strikes him. He and I are both total newbies&#8230;</p>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you&#8217;re into social media and have a Twitter account, you can now keep tabs on Cody there. His little paws will be tapping out messages over there whenever the mood strikes him. He and I are both total newbies to Twitterville, so if you can give us any advice on how to get the most out of it or add us to your Twitter list, that would be swell. You can follow Cody at <a title="Cody on Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/CodysCuentos" target="_self">Twitter.com/CodysCuentos</a>.</p>
